s you can find. Such cute stuff!',100,2,'2010-07-01 21:53:34','2010-09-10 22:07:28',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(640,202,'Couldn’t care less  what you wear. It’s a baseball game, not a fashion show! You\'re there to support the team.',225,3,'2010-07-01 21:53:54','2010-10-17 12:35:34',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(641,202,'Borrow a t-shirt from your husband or son, then buy a hat when you get to the stadium or when you get home go online to see what is on sale.',300,4,'2010-07-01 21:54:53','2010-07-07 12:56:21',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(642,203,'Gift? Who has time to think about shopping? There\'s so much to be done, like booking the restaurant, getting invitations printed, choosing decorations, planning a menu, deciding what filling to put in the cake, coordinating RSVPs, etc, etc.',225,1,'2010-07-01 21:57:16','2010-09-10 22:08:25',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(643,203,'OK, that\'s your department! The rest of the sisters can deal with the caterers. You know each anniversary and what gift corresponds with it. Your specialty is shopping for the exact right gift.',100,2,'2010-07-01 21:58:02','2010-10-20 12:08:04',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(644,203,'Sure, you’ll contribute toward the gift. Time\'s going to be tight with all the party preparations, but if your sisters need help shopping for a present, you’ll try to make time to go along.',150,3,'2010-07-01 21:58:25','2010-10-17 12:37:09',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(645,203,'You’ll go to your favorite website, which you have bookmarked, to look for cute and clever gift ideas for anniversaries.',300,4,'2010-07-01 21:58:46','2010-10-17 12:37:47',1,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(646,204,'Of course! But only if she fits into the schedule you already have mapped out for the sales. You\'re setting the alarm for 3 AM, grabbing your thermos of coffee, and heading out the door by 3:15 AM. No time fo