rate big payoffs for your emotional health. Start by taking small, simple steps that bring more peace into each day, which will help you develop a brighter outlook and more resilient personality. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSign up to receive your free Personalized&nbsp;Assessment based on the quiz you just completed. And then consider joining the MaxWell&nbsp;Daily club for access to your Personalized Plan.&nbsp;In it, you&rsquo;ll get dozens of specific steps to improve your emotional wellness plus recommendations on exactly how to develop a program that works for you. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>',800,999,1,'2009-01-13 07:17:27','2009-02-09 04:11:34',NULL),(1011,22,'','<p>You&rsquo;re in solid shape, emotionally. But you can take some simple steps that will generate more happiness on a day-to-day basis. Small changes will generate big payoffs for your emotional health, provided you focus on just the right goals. You&rsquo;re on your way to a brighter outlook and more resilient personality. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSign up to receive your free Personalized&nbsp;Assessment based on the quiz you just completed. And then consider joining the MaxWell&nbsp;Daily club for access to your Personalized Plan.&nbsp;In it, you&rsquo;ll get dozens of specific steps to improve your emotional wellness plus recommendations on exactly how to develop a program that works for you.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>',1000,1399,1,'2009-01-13 07:20:04','2009-02-09 04:11:20',NULL),(1012,22,'','<p>You&rsquo;re in excellent emotional health. You&rsquo;ve done great work in generating a resilient personality and bright outlook, but you can still gain more peace and clarity. The trick is to focus on the right stuff so your efforts are well rewarded.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSign up to receive your free Personalized&nbsp;Assessment based on the quiz you just completed. And then consider joining the MaxWell&nbsp;Daily club for access to your Personalized Plan.&nbsp;In it, you&rsquo;ll get dozens of ideas on how to improve your emotional wellness plus recommendations on exactly how to develop a program that works for you. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>',1400,1600,1,'2009-01-13 07:20:43','2009-02-09 04:11:53',NULL),(1013,25,'Revenue Survey Demo Recommendation 1','<p>Revenue Survey Demo Recommendation 1</p>',0,50,1,'2009-07-20 19:03:24','2009-07-20 19:03:39',NULL),(1014,26,'Recommendation 1 (edit)','<p>Recommendation Text 1</p>',0,0.5,1,'2010-02-03 20:26:40','2010-02-03 20:39:22',NULL),(1015,26,'Recommendation 2','<p>Recommendation Text 2 (edit)</p>',3,5,1,'2010-02-03 20:27:02','2010-02-03 20:39:36',NULL),(1016,26,'Recommendation 1a (edit)','<p>Recommendation 1a (edit)</p>',0.6,3,1,'2010-02-03 20:40:10','2010-02-03 20:40:10',NULL),(1017,27,'Quiz Reco','<p>0 means ....</p>\r\n<p>10 means...</p>',0,100,1,'2010-02-05 01:13:20','2010-02-05 01:13:20',NULL),(1036,35,'Quiz Recommendation','',0,1e+06,1,'2010-04-19 02:55:15','2010-04-19 02:55:15',NULL),(1037,36,'Recommendation 1','<p>PETCO recommendation</p>',0,5000,1,'2010-05-10 00:21:46','2010-05-10 00:21:46',NULL),(1038,99,'Generic Recommendation','<p>Generic Recommendation</p>',0,100000,1,'2010-05-26 23:28:06','2010-05-26 23:28:06',NULL),(1039,101,'Dummy','<p>&nbsp;None</p>',0,1e+06,1,'2010-07-16 15:40:17','2010-07-16 15:40:17',NULL),(1040,102,'None','<p>&nbsp;None</p>',1,1000,1,'2010-08-04 01:52:57','2010-08-04 01:52:57',NULL),(1041,103,'Dummy','<p>&nbsp;Dummy Result</p>',0,1e+06,1,'2010-09-22 17:37:31','2010-09-22 17:37:31',NULL),(1042,104,'Dummy','<p>&nbsp;Dummy</p>',0,1e+06,1,'2011-04-13 06:03:16','2011-04-13 06:03:16',NULL);
