u?',1,'2010-06-26 01:53:13','2010-07-06 15:37:04',NULL,NULL,'Like most of us, you grew up watching sitcoms. From the sublime to the ridiculous, the moms on these programs worked their way into our collective unconscious. Take this quiz to find out which TV mom you are most like',NULL),(44,7,'(Bhavan) - Job hunting style',0,'2010-07-16 14:08:47','2010-07-16 14:08:47',NULL,NULL,'',NULL),(99,4,'Generic Survey',1,'2010-05-26 22:29:24','2010-05-26 22:29:24',NULL,NULL,'Generic Survey',2),(101,4,'SignatureHomestyles',1,'2010-07-16 14:14:20','2010-07-16 14:14:20',NULL,NULL,'SignatureHomestyles',2),(102,4,'Casual Dining Survey',1,'2010-08-03 19:33:04','2010-08-03 19:33:04',NULL,NULL,'Generic questions used by RedRobin, etc.',2),(103,4,'TWE Survey',1,'2010-09-22 14:55:27','2010-09-22 14:55:27',NULL,NULL,'TWE Survey 10/01/2010',2),(104,4,'FBM Survey Quiz',1,'2011-04-13 04:28:11','2011-04-13 04:50:20',NULL,NULL,'FBM Survey Quiz',2);
